A list of things this game will not have:

Closed source elements
Distribution of leveling-up points to skills every damn time I level up
Collect X, take it to Z. Get bored at point Y and never play again
Eating/sleeping/gyming/BORING_STUPID_REAL_LIFE_SHIT
A static storyline
3D
Configured systems
Auto-leveled opponents


Stuff the game might have:

Windows/Mac/Linux/Android support
Built off an existing open source game engine, options:
    http://orx-project.org/
    http://getmoai.com/moai/
    http://libgdx.badlogicgames.com/
Replayability
Roguelike death frequency (may reconsider)
Easy to quit/continue_later
Minecraft-like auto-saving (consequences matter)
Reputation system that's not retarded
